data.description: Fears Mill community welcomes you to your new home! Gorgeous, LIKE NEW, 5 bedroom, 3.5 bathroom home nestled on almost half acre PREMIUM CORNER LOT awaits its next owner. Endless curb appeal, level driveway and landscaped sprawling yard - you can't miss it! Main level boasts an open two story foyer with natural light that energizes the space upon entry and exit. Spacious eat-in kitchen with breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances, paired with a OVERSIZED pantry (seriously, like a grocery store when full!), overlook your open family room, and separate dining room - great for entertaining! Large Junior Suite to make all of your sleepover guests feel special or could be used as a Teen or In-Law Suite. Additional half bathroom completes the main floor. Upstairs flaunts the truly MASTERFUL PRIMARY SUITE with fairytale balcony, sitting room, HIS and HER CLOSETS (to keep the peace, of course =), and spa-like bathroom with dual vanity, and separate shower and jetted tub! 3 more secondary bedrooms, full bathroom, and spacious laundry room complete the upper level.   *NEW ROOF (8/2023)**Kitchen flooring (7/2023)** and **Updated light fixtures throughout!** This home has it all!   Convenient to everything, yet private! 5 mins from downtown Hampton where you can enjoy a brewery, ice cream shop, restaurants, and festivals. Access to Atlanta Motor Speedway (10 mins), Tara Blvd (10 mins), and I-75 (15 mins).
